    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>游戏原本计划只发布英文版，不过我们会密切关注愿望单数量，并优先对需求量最大的语种开展本地化工作。所以，喜欢的话别忘了加入愿望单哦，感谢支持！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《奇幻橄榄球》是一款融合美式橄榄球和足球元素的回合制战术角色扮演游戏。在奇幻王国中，你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将率队征战女王之国，击败对手，打造冠军球队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/76d82195592b35abddcc40cd2d3584b9.poster.avif?t=1771799312\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/76d82195592b35abddcc40cd2d3584b9.webm?t=1771799312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/76d82195592b35abddcc40cd2d3584b9.mp4?t=1771799312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四对四回合制对战，为球队做决策，智取对手。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每名球员在其回合可移动并执行一次动作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺取控球权后，你可以传球，也可以带球冲向球门区，全看你的选择！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >率先攻入两球的球队获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对敌人造成伤害，增加他们失误或被击出场外的几率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远程施放魔法技能，或近身发动猛烈擒抱和铲断。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用特殊技能传球、治疗队友、快速移动、给己方施放增益或给对手减速。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善用地形优势，发挥球队最大潜力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征战女王之国16个独特赛场，不断为球队解锁强力新技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从八个不同位置选取球员组建球队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次行动都能获得经验值，提升等级和属性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术失误？别担心！内置的回退功能让你轻松重来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义规则的快速对战模式，可挑战电脑或好友。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心打造的90年代低面模风格赛场，复古感十足。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/f3ff99fbdbf92bae6fc45c2835c0d480.poster.avif?t=1771799312\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/f3ff99fbdbf92bae6fc45c2835c0d480.webm?t=1771799312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035460/extras/f3ff99fbdbf92bae6fc45c2835c0d480.mp4?t=1771799312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建你的梦之队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八个位置任你挑选，随意搭配。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平衡者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投掷者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突击者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施法者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阻挡者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >防守者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支援者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破局者</p></li></ul>",
